~ May Alexis be blessed for her kindness and understanding.
  Our new home is among horrible and deadly creatures, but
  those who pass never notice that the entrance is through
  those horrendous webs; some of them were woven by
  unquestionably repulsive creatures.

~ The nitrates which fill up the swamp possess a lethal
  power. I dare not detail the uses I have found for the
  saltpeter in this journal.  Needless to say, I am probably
  the only being on earth whose mining for this substance.

~ I worked through the night twice alread this week. Alexis
  has been fuming mad.  I'd better give her something nice
  after I've completed this project. But she has all the gold
  and precious metals any woman could ever want. What am I
  to do?
